paratype male (97, 98) and female (99, 100) fresh collection Honghu City (NHMHAU). 97, 99 dorsal; 98, 100 ventral. Scale line is 5 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="5BFD6657F819FF886BFB900419E7F83B" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/258013/files/figure.png" pageId="31" pageNumber="232" targetBox="[231,1372,203,1818]" targetPageId="31">
